---
import headshot from "../portfolio_images/headshot.jpg";
---

<div id="head-container">
  <h1 class="anitext">Chirag</h1>
  <h2 class="anitext">A Student of Life <br /> Lifetime learner</h2>
  <img
    id="headshot"
    src={headshot}
    alt="headshot"
  />

  <p>
    I’m a man who is trying to better his life by throwing himself into tireless
    work and skill development. I’m a total detail freak. I’m often ask lots of
    questions, and deliver quality works, always.
    <br />I am not fixed to a specific software or programming language and
    switch to what is best for the project.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  #headshot {
    height: 100vh;
    position: absolute;
    right: -15rem;
    top: 0;
    transform: translate3d(0, 0, -10px) scale(1.75);
    transform-style: preserve-3d;

    z-index: -100;
  }

  h1 {
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 160px;
    width: fit-content;
    margin: 20vh 0;
    /* position: relative; */
    /* top: 15vh; */
  }

  h2 {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 40px;
    width: fit-content;
    margin: 0;

    /* position: relative; */
    /* top: 35vh; */
  }

  p {
    /* position: absolute; */
    /* bottom: 0; */

    margin-top: 40vh;
    width: 60%;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 50px;
    text-decoration-line: underline;
  }

  #head-container {
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    padding-left: 8%;
    min-height: 200vh;
    /* z-index: -1000; */
  }
</style>
